Off duty?

00:26:20.300 --> 00:26:20.720
No.

00:26:20.720 --> 00:26:21.560
Location.

00:26:21.560 --> 00:26:25.211
So on duty you could carry a firearm.

00:26:25.211 --> 00:26:34.930
In the state of Illinois, you need a FOID and a CCW to carry a weapon off duty.

00:26:50.360 --> 00:26:50.730
But on duty you could.

00:26:50.730 --> 00:26:51.470
Correct.

00:26:51.470 --> 00:26:52.210
Wow.

00:26:52.210 --> 00:27:03.206
You know what's crazy about this is I don't know anything about him other than he says he loves America.

00:27:20.560 --> 00:27:20.880
The problem is he's not even a citizen.

00:27:20.880 --> 00:27:24.880
So he can't own a firearm legally in our country.

00:27:32.120 --> 00:27:32.480
But he's being given a firearm by the state of Illinois as a police officer.

00:27:33.560 --> 00:27:37.227
And apparently, all you have to have is work authorization.

00:27:37.227 --> 00:27:38.960
That is insane.

00:27:38.960 --> 00:27:47.308
You haven't even sworn allegiance to our country yet, and yet we're giving you a firearm.

00:27:47.308 --> 00:27:58.740
Now this guy may be a great guy, but how many others are working in our country as police officers who aren't great guys?

00:28:13.177 --> 00:28:13.594
I don't know if that bothers you, but it bothered me.

00:28:13.594 --> 00:28:15.679
That's insanity to me.

00:28:15.679 --> 00:28:29.996
You're giving somebody that can't even legally buy a firearm a badge and a gun and telling him he can be a police officer in our country, and he's not even a legal citizen.

00:28:42.200 --> 00:28:42.453
He just got over here and he said, 'I started in January.

00:28:42.453 --> 00:28:46.280
' Now he's been a police officer all this time.

00:28:46.280 --> 00:28:50.693
And I'm thinking, you're arresting people.

00:28:59.410 --> 00:28:59.845
I don't know.

00:28:59.845 --> 00:29:02.080
Does that just bother me?

00:29:02.080 --> 00:29:07.087
Did anybody else know this kind of stuff's going on?

00:29:07.087 --> 00:29:09.543
It's just interesting to me.

00:29:11.250 --> 00:29:23.795
I don't try to be a drama person, but I try to bring light to the darkness that's going on in our nation and why we are called to pray as a family.

00:29:40.435 --> 00:29:49.514
The importance of us coming together and assembling ourselves on this channel and praying for the nations, praying for that which is to come.

00:29:49.514 --> 00:29:54.160
Now, I'm going to hurry because I've already been 20 minutes.

00:29:54.160 --> 00:29:57.760
So, let's go over this last vision.

00:29:57.760 --> 00:30:02.692
Does anybody want to talk about what I saw?

00:30:02.692 --> 00:30:04.120
That was a 'wow'.

00:30:19.111 --> 00:30:19.382
As we were praying at the end of the broadcast, I felt in my spirit to keep praying.

00:30:26.829 --> 00:30:27.086
I just felt inside the Lord wasn't done.

00:30:32.520 --> 00:30:38.147
But as we kept pushing, I went over and I started going into a different kind of a tongue.

00:30:45.830 --> 00:31:02.410
And the Lord told me, 'I'm going to start to work with you with interpretation of tongues, and it will start out small, and it will grow and grow, and you'll understand when it's at a full manifestation.

00:31:02.410 --> 00:31:11.280
You'll understand everything in detail of what you're praying in the spirit just by hearing it.

00:31:11.280 --> 00:31:27.040
' And it will be like you press in and the Lord reveals and I hear the words—I hear what he's saying in my spirit.

00:31:41.600 --> 00:31:41.851
But in this, when I'm praying in the spirit, he said, 'You'll start to interpret all of it.

00:31:41.851 --> 00:32:04.097
' But as I was praying two days ago, I saw Jesus and he was wearing a beautiful robe like he always does, but he had a drum around his neck and he started drumming like a drummer boy.

00:32:04.097 --> 00:32:11.516
But he was drumming the drum and it was like a cry to come.

00:32:11.516 --> 00:32:24.240
Last time it was a horn and his voice turned into a horn, but this time it was making a noise like a drum.

00:32:24.240 --> 00:32:34.240
But he was marching with it and he went up to the first house and he was in Sweden.

00:32:37.289 --> 00:32:37.431
The Lord said, 'I'm in Europe.

00:32:37.431 --> 00:32:40.040
' I saw it was in Europe.

00:32:40.040 --> 00:32:57.987
And as the Lord would go to the houses, he went to each individual home and he was knocking on the door of the heart of the individual and he was inviting them to follow him.

00:32:57.987 --> 00:33:01.360
'Will you follow me?

00:33:01.360 --> 00:33:06.497
Will you be a part of this end-time army?

00:33:06.497 --> 00:33:18.760
' And as he would knock on the door, the people would open the door and they would be so excited to see that it was the Lord.

00:33:19.533 --> 00:33:28.400
I saw these old cottages with old wooden doors and Jesus would summon them, 'Come follow me, come follow me.

00:33:28.400 --> 00:33:45.410
' And they would get in line, one after another, and he went to each door and he was walking through this valley of life with green grass all around.

00:33:49.660 --> 00:33:54.320
I could see at the top of the mountains—the mountains were massive like the Swiss Alps, massive, beautiful snow-capped mountains.

00:33:54.320 --> 00:34:01.520
And he was walking through this valley, but there were houses all along the way.

00:34:15.480 --> 00:34:15.920
And Jesus would go up and knock on each and every single door.

00:34:15.920 --> 00:34:23.644
Now, some of the doors that he walked up to looked dilapidated.

00:34:24.134 --> 00:34:25.919
The shutters on the house were falling off.

00:34:25.919 --> 00:34:28.702
They looked like the hinges were broken.

00:34:28.702 --> 00:34:34.430
There were cobwebs in the corners.

00:34:36.000 --> 00:34:39.167
The lights weren't on in the house.

00:34:45.080 --> 00:34:45.476
And as he knocked on the house, no one would answer.

00:34:45.476 --> 00:34:54.040
So he looked around and looked at the house and he glanced at the eaves.

00:34:54.040 --> 00:34:58.373
He glanced at everything.

00:35:08.760 --> 00:35:09.255
And I saw him looking.

00:35:09.255 --> 00:35:23.820
He was looking at the ground and he was waiting patiently and no one would come to the door and all of a sudden he turned away and just kept on marching.

00:35:23.820 --> 00:35:25.771
He kept beating his drum.

00:35:27.291 --> 00:35:30.900
And as he went to each house, the people would line up behind him.

00:35:30.900 --> 00:35:44.140
Some of them had shorts and overalls on that were German, and I don't remember the name of them, but these people had nice cut hair and they were all excited.

00:35:44.140 --> 00:35:48.545
Some of them had bigger bellies than others, like all of us.

00:35:48.545 --> 00:35:50.680
Lederhosen?

00:35:50.680 --> 00:35:51.853
Lederhosen.

00:35:51.853 --> 00:35:52.825
Thanks.

00:35:52.825 --> 00:35:57.620
They were wearing those because he was going through Europe.

00:36:17.807 --> 00:36:18.293
I don't even know if people still wear that.

00:36:18.293 --> 00:36:20.240
Isn't it neat?

00:36:32.920 --> 00:36:33.292
But as he was walking on the path, it looked like a yellow brick road, but it wasn't.

00:36:42.138 --> 00:36:42.385
It was cobblestone.

00:36:43.326 --> 00:36:51.520
And I could see each stone was beautifully cut as he was walking through this valley.

00:36:51.520 --> 00:36:57.904
There were flowers and daffodils on the side of the road.

00:37:02.040 --> 00:37:05.311
And there were patches of them and they were all beautifully blooming and so beautiful.

00:37:19.270 --> 00:37:19.545
And as he walked down the path, the flowers would bow down before him.

00:37:21.931 --> 00:37:31.222
And all the flowers would lay prostrate on the ground, and then as he walked by, they all raised back up.

00:37:31.222 --> 00:37:38.520
But as our King Jesus walked by, even the flowers would bow down before our Father.

00:37:38.520 --> 00:37:47.310
You know the Bible says that if we don't praise him, the rocks will cry out.

00:38:06.573 --> 00:38:06.849
But I know that all creation gives praise to our King—the birds of the air, the lily of the valley.

00:38:06.849 --> 00:38:09.164
He is the lily of the valley.

00:38:09.164 --> 00:38:12.280
He is the fairest of ten thousand.

00:38:16.880 --> 00:38:32.863
And as I saw the waterfalls falling off the cliffs and the mountains and the snow caps because it looked like it was turning into spring, the Lord said, 'I want you to pay attention to these flowers for it is symbolic of something.

00:38:32.863 --> 00:38:36.540
' He said, 'Look into it.

00:38:36.540 --> 00:38:42.920
' So I've had so many people try to help.

00:38:56.535 --> 00:38:57.153
What does the daffodil represent?

00:39:06.650 --> 00:39:06.885
This is a representation of spring coming.

00:39:06.885 --> 00:39:11.236
The Holy Ghost is telling me a great harvest is coming.

00:39:11.236 --> 00:39:28.827
As I saw the people marching through the valley, joining up with Jesus in a single file line, following our friend, following our king, our maker, as he was going through the valley.

00:39:28.827 --> 00:39:35.247
As I watched him, he went all through Europe to each place.

00:39:43.008 --> 00:39:43.336
Then he went through the Middle East, down through Africa, through South America, and through America.

00:39:43.336 --> 00:39:50.800
He went around and was knocking on every one of our hearts: 'Will you let me in?

00:39:50.800 --> 00:39:53.550
Will you accept me as Lord and Savior?

00:39:53.550 --> 00:39:55.820
' But he was a gentleman about it.

00:39:55.820 --> 00:39:57.249
He waited a little bit.

00:39:57.249 --> 00:40:05.818
He looked around to see if the person would answer the door, but he didn't force his way in.

00:40:05.818 --> 00:40:14.880
He didn't knock the door down and say, 'You're getting saved, buddy.

00:40:14.880 --> 00:40:15.680
Get out here.

00:40:15.680 --> 00:40:17.080
Come on.

00:40:17.080 --> 00:40:20.320
We're going.

00:40:20.320 --> 00:40:23.316
' He waited patiently to see if they would answer.

00:40:23.316 --> 00:40:29.147
But as he waited, he sat there with expectation on his face.

00:40:29.147 --> 00:40:32.016
'Will you just let me in?

00:40:32.016 --> 00:40:37.000
I want to be your savior.

00:40:37.000 --> 00:40:41.795
I want you to follow me.

00:40:41.795 --> 00:40:43.055
Come follow me.

00:40:43.055 --> 00:40:49.240
' I figured this is how he did it with the disciples.

00:40:49.240 --> 00:40:54.650
'Come follow me.

00:40:54.650 --> 00:40:59.395
I'll make you a fisher of men.

00:40:59.395 --> 00:41:03.040
Come follow me, Matthew.

00:41:03.040 --> 00:41:12.720
' And as he would go through the towns and the places, the disciples followed him.

00:41:12.720 --> 00:41:17.940
'Will you be a disciple of Jesus Christ?

00:41:17.940 --> 00:41:24.980
' That's what I believe that vision was.

00:41:25.520 --> 00:41:27.056
It was so beautiful and so detailed.

00:41:29.151 --> 00:41:29.396
It changed me.

00:41:29.396 --> 00:41:36.916
But as it kept going, I heard, 'Woe, woe, woe, America.

00:41:36.916 --> 00:41:44.577
Woe, woe, woe, Miami.

00:41:44.577 --> 00:41:48.333
Woe, woe, woe, Los Angeles.

00:41:48.333 --> 00:41:53.728
' I saw a tsunami wave coming.

00:41:53.728 --> 00:41:56.024
I saw great destruction coming.

00:41:56.024 --> 00:42:03.429
There was an arrow that went from Miami all the way across the country to Los Angeles.

00:42:03.429 --> 00:42:10.950
As I was looking into this vision that the Lord was allowing me to see, I saw dead fish everywhere.

00:42:15.250 --> 00:42:15.485
I have never seen anything like this before.

00:42:16.149 --> 00:42:19.564
The very waters were all polluted with a red sludge.

00:42:19.564 --> 00:42:23.000
There were so many dead fish, whales, octopus—all of it.

00:42:23.000 --> 00:42:25.098
Everything was floating on the top.

00:42:25.098 --> 00:42:26.198
Disgusting.

00:42:26.198 --> 00:42:28.713
All dead.

00:42:28.713 --> 00:42:36.710
It was as far as the eye could see.

00:42:53.120 --> 00:42:53.507
It wasn't just on the shoreline, but they were dead all throughout the water.

00:42:57.249 --> 00:42:57.573
The water was littered with dead fish.

00:42:57.573 --> 00:43:02.600
I don't think any of them were alive.

00:43:02.600 --> 00:43:19.167
In the vision, I saw islands: Haiti, Jamaica, Grand Cayman, all of them.

00:43:19.167 --> 00:43:21.924
I was looking toward the south-southeast.

00:43:21.924 --> 00:43:32.887
As I was looking down, I could see the people, and there was so much stench and a raw flesh smell.

00:43:32.887 --> 00:43:42.544
People were so sick on those islands because of all the dead fish.

00:43:42.544 --> 00:43:46.150
It was causing disease and the smell.

00:43:50.260 --> 00:43:51.260
You could smell it in the vision.

00:43:51.260 --> 00:43:53.735
That's how tangible this vision was.

00:43:54.570 --> 00:44:00.040
I could see the dead fish washing on the shore, and the government didn't know what to do with them.

00:44:12.080 --> 00:44:12.320
People didn't know what to do because they were all washing in and you couldn't control it.

00:44:30.835 --> 00:44:31.140
There were literally hundreds of millions, if not billions, of dead fish everywhere—even Hawaii, Honolulu.

00:44:31.140 --> 00:44:34.240
I saw it all over.

00:44:34.240 --> 00:44:39.051
Then I saw Mark Zuckerberg, but his hair was a lot puffier.

00:44:44.440 --> 00:44:44.693
He was down in a bunker in the middle of the island.

00:44:46.424 --> 00:44:49.552
He was down in a fraidy hole, like a silo.

00:44:49.552 --> 00:44:55.048
I could see lights on around him.

00:44:55.048 --> 00:45:01.720
But as I panned across, the Lord allowed me to see people hiding in caves.

00:45:01.720 --> 00:45:09.980
I heard, 'The great and terrible day of the Lord.

00:45:09.980 --> 00:45:16.413
' Suddenly, I saw farmers, and they had their overalls, but all the land was not producing.

00:45:16.413 --> 00:45:19.314
There was great drought and famine.

00:45:31.787 --> 00:45:32.004
I could see them looking toward the south and the east, but they had a discouragement upon their faces like, 'What are we going to do?

00:45:32.004 --> 00:45:41.280
' As I looked to the sky, I saw the sky all around us was on fire.

00:45:41.280 --> 00:45:49.444
There was smoke and ash and flame in the air from volcanoes that were going off everywhere.

00:46:04.160 --> 00:46:04.560
I could see the smoke blotting out the sun, but the sun was trying to shine through.

00:46:10.609 --> 00:46:10.804
The ground was charred.

00:46:10.804 --> 00:46:13.710
Something looked wrong with the ground in this vision.

00:46:13.710 --> 00:46:19.375
As I looked to the east, I saw four massive angels in the water.

00:46:20.800 --> 00:46:28.504
I saw a massive waterfall coming out of the belly of the angels, pouring into the water below.

00:46:29.120 --> 00:46:32.895
The water was going into the oceans.

00:46:32.895 --> 00:46:35.287
Their skin was not skin; it looked like rain.

00:46:46.100 --> 00:46:46.800
You know whenever you see rain falling in the distance, and you can see blue streaks in the sky?

00:46:46.800 --> 00:46:53.950
That's the way the skin looked on these angels.

00:46:53.960 --> 00:46:57.840
There was no real tangibility; it was all rain, but there was an outline.

00:47:00.566 --> 00:47:11.280
The entire being of the angel was rain, a storm, and there was a major waterfall coming out of them, pouring into the ocean.

00:47:11.720 --> 00:47:14.048
I knew they were angels.

00:47:14.048 --> 00:47:18.884
Their faces had no features—it was just black around their eyes.

00:47:18.884 --> 00:47:21.900
You could get lost in that darkness.

00:47:21.900 --> 00:47:28.560
I've never seen anything like it.

00:47:29.751 --> 00:47:35.760
I saw one angel take a long pipe from his hand and put it to his lips.

00:47:35.760 --> 00:47:43.840
As he blew into this horn-looking thing, I said, 'It doesn't look like a ram's horn, like a shofar.

00:47:43.840 --> 00:47:48.380
' It was a long piece of golden pipe.

00:47:48.380 --> 00:47:52.116
As he blew into it, the whole earth shook.

00:47:52.116 --> 00:48:04.720
Not just one place had an earthquake, but as he blew into this horn, all of the earth shook at once.

00:48:09.840 --> 00:48:12.325
I heard the scripture: 'The earth will rock and reel like a drunkard.

00:48:12.325 --> 00:48:16.320
' The whole earth was trembling.

00:48:16.320 --> 00:48:21.240
He said, 'There will be no place to hide to escape the wrath to come, son.

00:48:21.240 --> 00:48:31.816
For they will hide in the caves and in their ditches, and they will not get away from the wrath which is to come.

00:48:31.816 --> 00:48:39.097
For this is the great and terrible day of the Lord.

00:48:39.097 --> 00:48:46.660
' As I looked across, I could see all of New York burning with fire.

00:48:46.660 --> 00:48:52.309
I could see a tsunami wave rushing into Miami.

00:48:52.309 --> 00:48:57.694
I could see all of the volcanoes in Hawaii going off at once.

00:48:57.694 --> 00:48:59.370
It was mass destruction.

00:48:59.705 --> 00:49:07.080
The whole earth was shaking violently, and they were wanting to hide in the caves and the rocks.

00:49:07.080 --> 00:49:13.039
They were fearful, but there was nothing they could do because the judgment was set.

00:49:13.039 --> 00:49:14.173
Dead fish were everywhere.

00:49:14.173 --> 00:49:18.097
There were no birds flying in the air because of the smoke.

00:49:27.800 --> 00:49:29.150
The grass was charred; everything looked burned up.

00:49:37.600 --> 00:49:38.069
I looked around at those farmers in their overalls, and they were very worried.

00:49:38.069 --> 00:49:40.411
This really bothered me.

00:49:55.020 --> 00:49:55.230
I didn't want to do a livestream last night.

00:50:08.858 --> 00:50:09.036
I told Diana, 'I'm going to meditate on this more and pray.

00:50:09.036 --> 00:50:11.176
Don't be so quick to make videos.

00:50:11.176 --> 00:50:16.200
' I had to process what I'd seen.

00:50:16.547 --> 00:50:20.417
I saw those angels and they really tripped me out.

00:50:20.417 --> 00:50:25.080
Diana said, 'I want to read Revelation to you, chapter 8.

00:50:25.080 --> 00:50:31.595
' She said there were four angels, and seven altogether, but four first and then three for a later time.

00:50:35.000 --> 00:50:37.406
And she goes, "Do you think this is what you were seeing, honey?

00:50:47.996 --> 00:50:48.204
" I said, "I don't know, babe.

00:50:48.204 --> 00:50:52.994
All I know is I saw these angels blowing these horns and all this stuff going on.

00:50:52.994 --> 00:50:58.905
" She goes, "Do you think it was the four coming out of the Euphrates River because they were water?

00:50:58.905 --> 00:50:59.950
" So, I don't know.

00:50:59.950 --> 00:51:04.307
All I know is that I am in awe.

00:51:04.307 --> 00:51:07.943
I'm in awe that God would allow me to see something like that.

00:51:16.760 --> 00:51:19.389
I thought it was really cool about the souls and all this stuff, but when I saw all this stuff happening with the sea again—the sea—and then the seas and the waves will roar.

00:51:19.389 --> 00:51:20.314
Remember that?

00:51:20.314 --> 00:51:23.589
And it was above the water; it was a sound.

00:51:23.589 --> 00:51:31.143
It wasn't that they were moving; it was deafeningly loud as the angel blew his horn.

00:51:31.143 --> 00:51:34.149
It was something upon the water.

00:51:34.149 --> 00:51:38.840
It sounded like you hear a tornado or a freight train.

00:51:45.787 --> 00:51:46.258
You can hear a train coming in the distance—that loud train coming, not the horn.

00:51:46.258 --> 00:51:50.640
It sounded like a loud noise, but it was deafening.

00:51:50.640 --> 00:51:54.250
It was so loud, and it was on the face of the water of the world.

00:52:08.440 --> 00:52:08.680
The seas and the waves were roaring.

00:52:15.940 --> 00:52:16.280
It was loud; it was a noise.

00:52:16.280 --> 00:52:21.987
All I know to tell you is that we're running out of time.

00:52:21.987 --> 00:52:37.560
As I see these things and I see the days approach, the Lord keeps warning me to tell you over and over again: it's time for you to come to Jesus.

00:52:37.560 --> 00:52:45.314
I say it over and over again and people say, "Brandon, why do you keep doing this?

00:52:45.314 --> 00:52:55.880
" Because there's an urgency in my spirit to warn you over and over again that you're running out of time.

00:52:55.880 --> 00:53:01.726
I don't know the time frame that Jesus Christ will come.

00:53:01.726 --> 00:53:08.940
No man knows the day or the hour, but we see that the time frame is speeding up.

00:53:08.940 --> 00:53:11.229
We can see, we can feel it.

00:53:11.229 --> 00:53:14.314
There's an urgency in the air.

00:53:15.720 --> 00:53:21.689
And my question for you is: do you know him?

00:53:28.480 --> 00:53:28.697
But more importantly, does he know you?

00:53:37.143 --> 00:53:39.994
I say this over and over again because it's so important as we keep going on with this channel and the Lord keeps showing us things more and more.

00:53:49.825 --> 00:53:51.107
It shakes me, and I have such an urgency to warn the people that 2026 will be the year of 1 Corinthians 5:5.

00:53:58.440 --> 00:54:05.740
And there will be so many people that have the seedtime and harvest accelerated that he doesn't want any of us to go to hell.

00:54:05.740 --> 00:54:10.272
He wants all of us to come to repentance.

00:54:10.272 --> 00:54:19.035
And it's time for the church to wake up because he said to me again, "Judgment begins in my house first.

00:54:19.035 --> 00:54:25.320
Brandon, judgment begins in my house first.

00:54:37.359 --> 00:54:37.569
It's time to come to Jesus.

00:54:38.830 --> 00:54:39.040
It's time.

00:54:39.040 --> 00:54:42.640
" But he is knocking on your heart even again tonight.

00:54:42.640 --> 00:54:44.789
Do you know my friend Jesus?

00:54:48.960 --> 00:54:55.383
You may be here tonight and you say, "Brandon, I hear you and you really scared me.

00:54:55.383 --> 00:54:58.895
" I'm not trying to scare you.

00:54:58.895 --> 00:55:01.067
I'm trying to prepare you.

